          <p>MR. MACMASTER : I also want to make a point, in the early 2000s - I know that government has - I talked about the debt already, and I want to mention something about taxes. I actually had an e-mail from a constituent, Dr. Chiasson. I'm going to read it, and I will table it. He's feeling as though our taxes are too high.</p>
        </speech>
